request.description:
Get profile image presigned URL.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Profile image fetched successfully",
  "data": { "userProfileImage": "<presigned_url>" }
}
```

Get government ID info (Freelancer only).

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "govtIdImage": "<presigned_url>",
    "gov_id_type": "aadhar",
    "gov_id_number": "1234...",
    "verification_status": "PENDING"
  }
}
```

Get all services listed by the authenticated freelancer. Services are grouped by `service_name`.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Services fetched successfully",
  "data": [
    {
      "service_name": "Web Development",
      "service_options": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "plan_type": "basic",
          "service_description": "...",
          "service_price": 5000,
          "delivery_time": "5-7 days",
          "thumbnail_file": "<presigned_url>",
          "is_active": true,
          "created_at": "...",
          "updated_at": "..."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

Get all portfolio items grouped by service type.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "Web Development": [...],
    "Video Editing": [...]
  },
  "message": "portfolio data found"
}
```

Add new portfolio items (images or videos).

