request.description:
Get freelancer suggestions for a specific service request. Wishlisted freelancers are sorted to the top.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": [
    {
      "freelancer_id": 5,
      "freelancer_full_name": "John Doe",
      "profile_image_url": "<presigned_url>",
      "freelancer_thumbnail_image": "<presigned_url>",
      "rating": 4.8,
      "profile_title": "Web Developer",
      "in_wishlist": true
    }
  ],
  "pagination": { "currentPage": 1, "totalPages": 2, "totalCount": 15, "limit": 10 }
}
```

